##****---> Vim
# https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/Vim.gitignore
# If you do not set 'directory', they are created in the current directory.
# See ":help swap-file" in recover.txt.  Also see
# <https://stackoverflow.com/a/38023956>
[._]*.s[a-v][a-z]
[._]*.sw[a-p]
[._]s[a-rt-v][a-z]
[._]ss[a-gi-z]
[._]sw[a-p]
# Vim backup and undo files respectively.  Just in case some-
# one is evil enough to create them in the CURRENT directory?
*~
*.un~
